              </msItem>
            </msItem>
            <msItem xml:id="a9" n="11">
              <locus from="195b"/>
              <author>Severus</author>
              <title xml:lang="en">The Order of Baptism, of <persName>Severus</persName></title>
              <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܬܘܒ ܒܝܕ ܐܠܗܐ ܟܬ݁ܒܝܢܢ ܥܡܕܐ ܏ܩܕ ܕܡܪܝ ܣܐܘܪܐܘܣ ܦܛ܏ܪܝ ܒܟܠܗܝܢ ܐܝܠܝܢ ܕܡܬܒ̈ܥܝܢ ܠܗ</rubric>
